On ubuntu149 spyder5 is in /usr/bin/spyder5 and works on all envs.

However, to run a specific environment in spyder (for example deeplearn) then in spyder5 do:

```
Preferences > Python interpreter > Use the following interpreter:  /home/stefan/anaconda3/envs/deeplearn/bin/python
```
